Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A racing second hand,\Na shooting comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan's logic works great on\Nhearts tired by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.68,0:00:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's case is a stalker!\NLet's think about what bothers people!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:57.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Stalker Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Stalker Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The air's so fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is nice in\Nthe early morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Today is\Nperfect walking weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was still dark when you woke\Nme up. I didn't get enough sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guts-Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to drink something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sleepy I can't keep up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two came out! I'm so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure there\Nwasn't one already there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't drink it if I were you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are no signs\Nof it being opened,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and nothing looks\Nout of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't smell strange, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone probably just forgot\Nit after buying a bunch of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Get an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guts-Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Did you drink that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it have been poisoned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deceased is Nagai\NTatsuya-{\i1}san{\i0}, 26.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lived on 3rd Street\Nin Midori-dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two train stops from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought I saw\Nhim somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's paint on his shoulder...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poison in the Guts-Man might\Nbe an organic phosphate compound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Organic phosphate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Small amounts cause\Nnausea or drooling,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while large amounts result\Nin respiratory failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure. This was\Nan indiscriminate murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Mori-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer placed the poisoned\NGuts-Man in the corner like so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Nagai-{\i1}san {\i0}stopped by\Nand bought a Guts-Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was the poisoned one\Nhe took, not the one he purchased.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after drinking it, the poison\Ntook effect and he collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is there proof the killer put\Nthe poisoned Guts-Man in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought a Guts-Man here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I did, I found an\Nextra bottle down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, there's a seal on\Nthat Guts-Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for a special campaign,\Nbut it ended three days ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof, there aren't\Nany on your bottles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor on this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. This may\Nserve as a vital clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered! I stopped\Nand questioned that man before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was about three weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman in an apartment up\Nahead reported being troubled
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by a creepy man who\Nconstantly followed her around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I found\Nthis man loitering out in front!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means he was a stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He followed\Nher because he liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he hadn't actually done anything,\Nso I gave him a stern warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was his job?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was studying\Nfor entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that woman's\Napartment near here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just past where he died...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe he was heading\Nthere again? Or following her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she didn't report\Nanything since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I figured he had\Nstopped following her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go\Ntalk to her for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He consumed a poisoned\Nenergy drink only forty minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon my asking,\Nbut where were you at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forty minutes ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had just gotten home...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I work at a restaurant in Haido.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:08:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We close up at 4:00,\Nso I left around 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you take the train\Nto Beika Station?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And did you walk home from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means it's just as Conan said...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us see your map.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nishitani-{\i1}san{\i0}. Please show us\Nwhat route you took coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went from the station like so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She passed by the vending machine\Nand the spot where he collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagai-{\i1}san{\i0} collapsed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nhe was following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was so relieved once he\Ndisappeared after he was warned!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she really not realize\Nshe was being followed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The windows and door\Nhave extra locks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she even has\Ndefense spray ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were these merely from when\Nshe was afraid of her stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an organic phosphate\Ncompound in the Guts-Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Nagai-{\i1}san{\i0}'s fingerprints\Nwere found on the bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's very likely\Nthe killer prepared it in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you determine where that\NGuts-Man bottle was purchased?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, but if it\Nwas from that machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then it was bought between yesterday\Nafternoon and seven days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, the company replaced\Nall the bottles with seal-less ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagai-{\i1}san{\i0}'s mother recently\Nmoved here from Shizuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I checked her\Napartment and found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photos of that woman we spoke to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they all seem to be sneak shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I visited Nishitani-{\i1}san\N{\i0}again before coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had no idea\Nshe was photographed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed extremely shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the same apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not a restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She lived in Yokohama,\Nwhere she worked at a bakery
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and dreamed of\Nopening her own store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she move here\Nto escape Nagai-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she couldn't sleep due to fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:11:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she started working\Nnights at a restaurant instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must've been so scared. Poor girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Nagai-{\i1}san {\i0}received money\Nfrom his father, an ironsmith,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he didn't need to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning he could follow\Nher whenever he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one lousy man\Nshe got caught up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she really not know\Nshe was being followed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree. There's something about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying she poisoned\Nthe Guts-Man and had him drink it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't rule it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps she knew\Nshe was being followed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bought a Guts-Man from that machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and left the poisoned\None when she picked it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Nagai-{\i1}san {\i0}also bought\None and grabbed the wrong one--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:12:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was no guarantee\Nhe'd buy the same drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're forgetting\Nsomething important. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See how the bottom ring is cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody would drink it if they saw\Nthe cap had already been undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the killer didn't\Nleave it in that vending machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now nothing makes sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, one other thing\Nabout Nagai-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His neighbors saw him leave his\Napartment around 10:00 last night
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a small bag in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was empty-handed\Nwhen he collapsed this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might have nothing to do with\Nthe incident, but it bothers me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:13:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there a way she could've\Nhad him drink an opened Guts-Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't drink any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Let's swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna stay here a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go swim then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're after the rest\Nof her cola, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right! That's crazy talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a swim,\NMitsuhiko-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea, Genta-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. Kids acting like perverts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I've figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how it was done,\Nbut there's no proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you questioning people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping to learn that the\Nvictim bought the Guts-Man here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you check the fingerprints\Non the coins in the vending machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but we didn't\Nfind the victim's prints.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we did find two coins totaling\N110 yen that had been wiped clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the killer did\Nbuy the Guts-Man here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only this had\Nbeen a bigger shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you'll catch\N'em on surveillance video...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Video? What if-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, did you check everything\NNagai-{\i1}san {\i0}was carrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was he carrying?\NMr. Mori asked me to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:15:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wallet, a license, cigarettes,\Nan apartment key, and a lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lighter?! What kind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It had a flip top and was a\Nlittle bigger than normal ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We returned it to\Nthe victim's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The paint that was on the victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister! Where did\Nyou get that paint?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}kun{\i0}. Megure here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't you call me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about?\NI need to leave for work...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! It appears I called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's started! Please continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nishitani-{\i1}san{\i0}.\NPlease tell work you won't be in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're the one who\Npoisoned and killed Nagai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That morning, you knew\NNagai-{\i1}san {\i0}was following you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you bought a Guts-Man\Nfrom that vending machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us call that Bottle A.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You then took your\Npre-prepared Bottle B
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretended to pick up\NBottle A as he watched on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You removed the cap\Nand drank it as you walked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you put a closed bottle on a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was not the Bottle B\Nwhich you had just drunk;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was yet another bottle you had\Nprepared in advance: Bottle C.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, stalkers are known\Nto collect their prey's belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Nagai-{\i1}san {\i0}naturally\Ntook Guts-Man Bottle C.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He found a large amount\Nof the drink left inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As he was infatuated with you,\Nhe happily drank it down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...unaware it had been poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason you left the\NGuts-Man in the machine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was to make it look like\Nan indiscriminate murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fingerprints were absent\Nfrom the coins used to buy Bottle A
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and from empty Bottle C
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you likely put glue on\Nyour fingers in the station restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we first visited, she slyly\Nrubbed something off her fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was dried glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unnatural to wear\Ngloves this time of year,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and holding the bottle in a tissue\Nwould've roused his suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you used glue instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Theorize all you want.\NYou have no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you didn't know he\Nwas secretly photographing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't blame you; he was\Nusing a customized camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A customized camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:19:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This lighter works like normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but slide this and it becomes a camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This button works the shutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was good with his hands,\Nlike his skilled ironsmith father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Closer inspection of those\Nphotographs will show
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that there is a seal\Non the Guts-Man there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The special campaign seal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you said, all the Guts-Man\Nbottles in that vending machine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were replaced with new, seal-less\Nbottles yesterday afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he would kill me if I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One week ago, when I walked\Ndown the station stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His look said, "How dare you\Ntell the police! I'm gonna kill you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I felt my only\Nchoice was to kill him first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector. It's a fact that\NNagai-{\i1}san {\i0}planned to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the bag behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It belonged to Nagai-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was hidden by a nearby lamppost\Nthat had been freshly painted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have a look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagai-{\i1}san {\i0}probably planned to\Nget the bag when she came home,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wait for his chance to get inside\Nby cutting a hole in the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then kill her with that knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she was almost--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't hold up as self-defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll likely get off\Non mitigating circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nishitani-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Atone for your sin\Nas quickly as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then continue toward your\Ndream of running your own bakery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still so very young.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This case really made me think,\Nespecially about stalkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do get clients who\Ntalk about being followed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or receiving silent phone calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proving this kind of crime is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police won't do much,\Nbut even if they do do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the instant the crazed person\Nfinds out you're strongly repulsed,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they can turn into\Na full-fledged criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! Nobody'd ever\Ngo crazy for a shrew like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.45,0:24:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never wanna be on her bad side!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:25.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.67,0:24:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.72,0:24:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no blood around\Na part of his wrist!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.89,0:24:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspects are triplets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:31.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Triplets Villa Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.06,0:24:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.57,0:24:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Triplets Villa Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.17,0:24:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.67,0:24:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Home Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.46,0:24:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode we're tricked by triplets.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.00,0:24:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh so maddening.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osomatsu is about sextuplets.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.64,0:24:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
